%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-nh%C3%A2n-chi%C3%AAm-b%C3%A1i-%E1%BB%A8c-Trai-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-t%E1%BB%AB-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-msUyNhJQFj9LjuxPaLAqNg">Kinh kiến trung thu đồng nhân chiêm bái Ức Trai tiên sinh từ đường - 京見中秋同人瞻拜抑齋先生祠堂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C3%B5-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Tri%E1%BB%83n/author-Thszj0g9ZmpwDppNNv3yLQ">Võ Khắc Triển</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-t%C3%ACnh-bi%E1%BB%83u/poem-AGKUOTf4MNBoRtTrY2zw2A">Trần tình biểu - 陳情表</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt/author-2WZpsdSFEWvTQerf8uTifQ">Lý Mật</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BB%B3-b%C3%A0-h%C3%A0nh/poem-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Tỳ bà hành - 琵琶行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/V%C3%A3n-xu%C3%A2n/poem-7IQ0KulSuJ-K5GAF2zQiFw">Vãn xuân - 晚春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/author-mXDKUZpgHTE66OhltBCLIw">Hàn Dũ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
